_sText:
De_brewpub_BETA
Map created for the US Beer Drinking Team - www.breweryservers.com
Beta version of the map for testing and de-bugging
There are many custom textures and models, and the map has been fully optimized for very smooth gameplay. The final version will also include an optimized nav file with place names and smart bots. Also includes an overview/radar.

The layout is somewhat chaotic (there are many ways to flank/sneak around) but still very tactical. Just about every gun and style of play is accommodated with a few long areas for sniping, many close areas for short-range combat and everything in-between.
